EIS measurements were conducted on pure and boron-doped titania in the wide potential range. In accordance to proposed approach for interpretation of EIS spectra registered for TiO2 nanotube arrays [8], Mott-Schottky analysis was performed. Thus, the plot shown in Fig. 8 was prepared on the basis of relation given as follows:21C2=2qεε0NDE−Efb−kTq\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
